# Timeout Roulette Leaderboard for The Shining One

This project provides a leaderboard for the Timeout Roulette game by The Shining One. It is essential to have the Timeout Roulette installed for this leaderboard to function properly.

## Installation

To install this leaderboard in Streamer.bot:

1. **Import the .sb file:** 
   - You can import the provided .sb file directly into Streamer.bot by going to the "Import" menu and selecting the file.
   - Alternatively, you can copy the import code and paste it directly into the "Import" section of Streamer.bot.

2. **Customization:**
   - The text messages used within the leaderboard can be easily customized in the action named `TSO::Roulette[Config_Text]`.
   - The names of the commands and who has access to them (e.g., mods only) can also be easily modified to suit your needs.

## Commands

- `!roulettelb` - Displays the top 3 users with the most losses in the roulette and their total timeout duration.
- `!roulettereset` (Mods only) - Resets the entire leaderboard.
- `!roulettereset [username]` (Mods only) - Resets the data for the specified username.

The names of the commands and who has access to them can be easily customized.
